Package tps.tp1.pack2Arrays

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    P01ArrayIntsInit
    O programa P01ArrayIntsInit declara um array com 10 inteiros e inicializa esse array com 10 valores escolhidos e introduzidos pelo utilizador (e.g., new int[]{5, 2, 90, ...}).
    P02ArraysExtractUniqsAndReps
    P02ArraysExtractUniqsAndReps encapsulates a program that starts by declaring two arrays (a and b) composed by ten integer numbers that are randomly selected from a uniform distribution within the following interval: [0, 20].
    P03WheelOfNames
    P03WheelOfNames encapsulates a program that starts by asking the user for an input of ten full names, with one full name per line and each line having up to 120 characters.
    P04FourInaRow  
    P05BitmapTransform
    Apply border to the image
